<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose lg:prose-lg text-gray-700">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p>
      At Hebron Matriculation Higher Secondary School, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.
    </p>

    <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>
      We do not collect any personal information from you unless you voluntarily provide it to us through forms (e.g., contact forms, alumni registration).
    </p>

    <h3>Cookies</h3>
    <p>
      Our website may use cookies to improve your browsing experience. You can choose to accept or decline cookies through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h3>External Links</h3>
    <p>
      Our website may contain links to other websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of such external sites.
    </p>

    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at hebronngl@yahoo.com.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
